  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The lung is at risk for ischemic insults during total cardiopulmonary bypass because lung
      perfusion is maintained solely by the bronchial arterial system
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study will be performed in the pediatric cardiothoracic unit, pediatric Assiut University
      Hospital. After obtaining approval from the local ethics committee and written informed
      parents consent 60 patients will be included in this study according to the following
      criteria:
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
